{"tid":326932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"申 訴 專 員 不 調 查 選 民 資 料 失 竊","createTime":"2017-07-18T11:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T11:32:20.000Z","uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c46d23df52ae907eb47d154780acff9b74428a84","tid":326932,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"申訴專員不調查選民資料失竊<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=228839&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D228839%26refer%3Dshare&d=DNbAz9IKmuUlXoNkJJ8oYjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b981bf5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D228839%26refer%3Dshare&h=7607cf61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=228839&amp;refer=share</a>"},{"pid":"a152fd219144c0899afb8710bb3c51f12c3da793","tid":326932,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】選舉事務處在特首選舉遺失兩部電腦，申訴專員公署表示不會調查。<br />\n<br />\n申訴專員公署解釋，政制及內地事務局等部門已先後發表三份報告，涵蓋多項改善建議，認為無須再主動調查事件。不過，公署仍然非常關注為何選舉事務處容許職員，將載有全港選民資料的電腦帶到亞博後備場地，而且存放在欠缺適當保安的房間，批評當局因循跟隨過往做法，管理層部署不周，監督不力，要為事件承擔責任。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權沒有回應會否處分有關職員，只表示已盡力跟進建議。"},{"pid":"b984ec3a184a330404b6d104f1bb1d25f144baf5","tid":326932,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"身有屎"}]}